{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bface6358d","title":"毛泽东对《这是政治战线上和思想战线上的社会主义革命》一文的批语和修改时加写的一段话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c1039f3774","index":0,"year":1957,"month":9,"day":15,"articleId":"bface6358d"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e35e5b870b","type":"title","text":"毛泽东对《这是政治战线上和思想战线上的社会主义革命》一文的批语和修改时加写的一段话","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bface6358d"},{"id":"014e483741","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bface6358d"},{"id":"68dcdc4c19","type":"paragraph","text":"退胡乔木同志。此件可用。请送刘、邓、伯达、定一再加斟酌。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bface6358d"},{"id":"1618f15afb","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东九月十五日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bface6358d"},{"id":"0ff54b71c6","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bface6358d"},{"id":"e2c534efa8","type":"paragraph","text":"我们现在所说的社会主义革命，许多时候叫作社会主义改造。在一九五六年，在经济制度方面，即在生产关系方面，主要是在生产资料所有制方面的社会主义改造，基本上完成了(没有最后完成)，人的改造则没有完成。而资产阶级右派分子则最坚决地反对这种改造。中国共产党曾经再三再四地指出人的改造的必要性和可能性，可是无法说服反动的资产阶级右派。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bface6358d"},{"id":"9c5a79b9ca","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：根据一九五七年九月十八日《人民日报》。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bface6358d"}],"page":{"id":"3dbaff9749","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bface6358d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}